document_title: Left testicular pain: Causes, symptoms and prevention
subsection_content: Left testicle pain is a painful condition that only occurs in the left testicle and is completely normal on the opposite side. This phenomenon is often rare but can still be a warning sign of some serious problems that need to be detected and treated early. (first)
